<item>
            <title>[DERBY-91] XA .sql tests fail with jar files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-91</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A handful of SQL tests such as jdbcapi/xaAnotherTest.sql fail when run against the jar files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The output contains lines like&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;JAVA ERROR: java.lang.NullPointerException&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for the ij XA testing commands like xa_datasource&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like the derbytools.jar is missing the class&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.derby.impl.tools.ij.xaHelper&lt;br/&gt;
since it is loaded indirectly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
